<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

    <PropertyGroup>
        <Authors>Alastair Lundy</Authors>
        <Company />
        <Description>Cross-platform Operating System Detection, Operating System Version Detection, Apple Silicon Mac Detection, programmatic .NET Runtime ID Generation, and more. For a full list of features please visit: https://github.com/NeverSpyTech/PlatformKit/blob/main/docs/FeatureComparisonByPlatform.md</Description>
        <Copyright>Copyright (c) Alastair Lundy 2018-2024</Copyright>
        <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/alastairlundy/PlatformKit/</RepositoryUrl>
        <PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>true</PackageRequireLicenseAcceptance>
        <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
        <PackOnBuild>true</PackOnBuild>
        <PackageId>PlatformKit</PackageId>
        <Owners>AlastairLundy</Owners>
        <Summary>PlatformKit is a library dealing with Platform specific code, platform specific issues, and platform detection in C# .NET Core.</Summary>
        <PackageTags>platform detection, CSharp,</PackageTags>
        <Title>PlatformKit</Title>
        <PackageReleaseNotes>## Changes since 3.x

### Additions
* Added ``StringExtensions`` extension class
* Added ``VersionExtensions`` extensions class
* Added overloads to the ``IsAtLeastVersion`` methods in WindowsAnalyzer and MacOsAnalyzer to use System.Version objects as parameters.

### Changes
* Changed ``IsAtLeastWindowsVersion`` method to ``IsAtLeastVersion``
* Changed ``IsAtLeastMacOsVersion`` method to ``IsAtLeastVersion`` 
* Made the ``IsWindows``, ``IsMac``, ``IsLinux``, and ``IsFreeBSD`` methods internal only - .NET Standard 2.0 projects needing access to these methods should add the ``PlatformKit.Classic.OSDetection`` nuget package.

### Removals
* Removed ``FreeBSDAnalyzer`` class - Please use the ``FreeBsdAnalyzer`` class instead.
* Removed ``MacOSAnalyzer class - Please use the ``MacOsAnalyzer`` class instead.
* Removed the ``GetOSPlatform`` method from ``OSAnalyzer``</PackageReleaseNotes>
   <Product>PlatformKit</Product>
        <LangVersion>default</LangVersion>
        <AutoGenerateBindingRedirects>true</AutoGenerateBindingRedirects>
